---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro'
import Header from '../components/Header.astro'
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro'
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts'
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header title={SITE_TITLE} />
    <main>
      <h1>
        🤡 <span
          style="
        background: -webkit-linear-gradient(315deg,#647eff 25%,#42d392);
        background-clip: text;
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent
      "
          >Hello, It's me!</span>
      </h1>
      <p>中文：</p>
      <p>
        大家好，我是
        zouhang，一个来自中国的软件工程师，目前居住在北京。我的主要工作是开发和维护大型的应用系统。我在软件开发方面拥有多年的经验，掌握了多种编程语言，例如
        JavaScript、TypeScript、Python、Golang 等。热爱分享，喜欢创造工具服务开发者。
        除了我的职业技能，我对云服务、人工智能也很感兴趣。我正在学习云服务、AIGC 等相关的知识，并在我的 GitHub
        上分享我的学习笔记和项目。
        在我的空闲时间，我也喜欢健身和旅游。我认为健身可以帮助我保持身体健康，旅游则可以帮助我放松身心，在忙碌的工作后获得新的思路和灵感。
        感谢您花时间了解我，我期待着和您交流和合作！
      </p>
      <p>English:</p>
      <p>
        Hello everyone,I'm zouhang, a software engineer from China currently residing in Beijing. My primary work involves developing and maintaining large-scale application systems. With years of experience in software development, I'm proficient in various programming languages such as JavaScript, TypeScript, Python, and Golang. I have a passion for sharing knowledge and enjoy creating tools to serve developers.
Apart from my professional skills, I have a keen interest in cloud services and artificial intelligence. I'm currently learning about cloud services, AIGC, and related topics, and I share my study notes and projects on my GitHub.
During my leisure time, I also enjoy fitness and traveling. I believe fitness helps me maintain physical health, while traveling helps me relax and gain new perspectives and inspiration after busy work schedules.
Thank you for taking the time to learn about me. I look forward to communicating and collaborating with you!
      </p>
      <em style="text-align: right; margin-left: auto; display: block; font-weight: bold;">via: ChatGPT</em>
      <p>
        <span
          style="
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            background: -webkit-linear-gradient(315deg,#42d392 25%,#647eff);
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent
          "
          >Contact me if you have a remote job :)</span
        >
        <span><a href="mailto:zouhangsweet@gmail.com">Send me an Email</a>.</span>
      </p>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
